casebody.data:
ALSTON v. DIRECTOR OF PATUXENT INSTITUTION [App. No. 14,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided September 20, 1966.

Before Hammond, C. J., and Hornly, Marbury, OppPn-HkiMBR, Barnes and McWilliams, JJ.

*714Per Curiam.

For the reasons assigned by Judge Cullen in the court below, the application for leave to appeal must be denied.

Application denied.
